thread.title: Russia's retaliation: Scores of Western diplomats expelled

title: Russia's retaliation: Scores of Western diplomats expelled
text:
Russia's retaliation: Scores of Western diplomats expelled   01:02 
Russia has fulfilled its promise to expel Western diplomats as retaliation for similar measures employed against them by Britain and its allies in the wake of the Sergei Skripal incident. Matthew Larotonda reports.
